Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.09,0:00:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all people,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,over the lives of everyone in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she chose the lives of the six of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.59,0:00:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! Get off the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fight for you no matter\Nwho we're up against!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.63,0:01:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you didn't make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right! Now let's move forward{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with the sun always in our hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As power passes through our clasped hands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}let's grab hold of our wishes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:02:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Working together, let's ride the giant waves{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.05,0:02:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be a journey fraught with injury{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but what you cherish most will be right there{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.43,0:02:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if you get into a jam{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll always be there to protect you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right! Now let's move forward{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with the sun always in our hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and gaze at the light beyond{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we gather up the pieces of our dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they'll make a map leading to tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So let's grab hold of our wishes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}under the same flag-- together, we're one{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One Piece{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:28.10,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Sanji Barges In! Sea Train Battle in the Storm!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow... Seriously, what's that man thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what he's thinking,\Nthat train was for Government use,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he'll get caught and it'll all be over for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? That's Galley-La's... Paul...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be thoughtless!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like there's something\Ngoing on between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Train stations are a place for\Npeople to meet or part ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As station employees, we should\Nquietly watch over them, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quietly, got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The train left quite a bit early, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the passengers were already here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the sea started getting\Nrougher than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we thought Aqua\NLaguna would come very soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we moved up the departure time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is dangerous, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should evacuate to\Nthe shipbuilding island soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That lady, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:05:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you... Once the train\Nhas left, we can't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not easy to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this Enies Lobby place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... well, I do understand how you feel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she was angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those idiots from the Government!\NThey're not gonna get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let us borrow a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge and strong ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to sail out\Nwhen the sea is like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such stupid stuff when you\Ndon't know how awful Aqua Laguna is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will make it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a whole other level from the\Ntype of storm surge you're thinking of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea will now get terribly rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can no longer sail out! If you did,\Nyou'd basically be sailing to your deaths!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Robin, too, laid down her life for us and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paulie-san! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We almost got dragged into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that. That big schedule\Nboard got torn apart by a wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like this has ever happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the power of this ebbing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:07:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already this strong\Nwhen it's only approaching?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The speed of the waves of\Nthis Aqua Laguna are abnormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Is the sea train Robin is on okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll probably get through the stormy\Narea right before the storm surge hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless it gets hit directly, it'll make\Nit through most of the big waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An inconspicuous letter\Nwas left in the station plaza.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably from one of your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter...? From whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised that you found such a small thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! It was left here in\Nan inconspicuous manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:46.20,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nami-san! Please read this!\N(Those other than Nami-san don't\Nhave to read it, since they're idiots.)"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... hold on a sec. The first half\Nis just a pointless love letter, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:08:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said it's a love letter.\NThe third man has appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Judging from the situation,\Nthe third man is actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is the important part.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P.S. Since I saw Robin-chan on the\N11 o'clock train, I'll get on board, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Sanji-kun got on that train?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, a big thug with a ducktail... Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one like that except Franky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, there's no one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fourth man... And to think\Nthat the fifth man is Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor Paulie-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it'd be better if he flatly gives up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... also, this was with that letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be at least one\Ntransponder snail in the sea train.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll get in touch with you as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to always keep this portable\Ntransponder snail I got in town with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Think of it as\Nyour dear beloved San--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So he'll call this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he foresaw where Nico Robin\Nwas going to be? That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:20.18,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nami-san! Please read this!\N(Those other than Nami-san don't\Nhave to read it, since they're idiots.)"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, Robin has Sanji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.64,0:09:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll definitely go to Enies Lobby, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... I can't even have a smoke here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?! So Sanji went\Nto the station after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp is on the same train, too. I'm glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:10:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, anyway, no matter what means\Nwe take to follow the sea train,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can't do anything unless\Nwe find Luffy and Zoro first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mistaken about the direction\Nthey flew to. So search those areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please help us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, how should I quietly infiltrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What a crazy storm outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Collier Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw his kick earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's no ordinary civilian!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...something like that so openly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll make me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't a compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's mocking us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let Lucci-san know that\Na suspicious man infiltrated!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't something that\Nwe need to bother CP9 with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how violent the suspicious man is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no need to fear, because in this car...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! It's smoky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you've got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerry-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a champion on a South Blue\Nisland where karate is popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'm a boxing champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.03,0:12:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, do karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can make a comment like\Nthat after you see my punches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerry... Aurora Flicker... Jab!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Jerry-san! The enemy is behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? He escaped?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid! Just because I'm so tall,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't think that I'm at a\Ndisadvantage in this small car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've been warned\Nby someone from between their legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My boxing rather puts me at\Nan advantage in a narrow space.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a yoga style!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoga one, two! One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your reach has gotten shorter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I made it look like, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Drop Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're ignoring the rules of boxing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brochette!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, the one who leads Government\Nofficials in car #7, the very last car, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order of increasing strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the one who leads forty\Nmarines in car #5 is T-Bone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a Navy Headquarters'\NCaptain and former knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, the one standing by in car #4 is Wanze,\Na martial artist from Cipher Pol No. 7,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who is also the head steward on this trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the one standing by in car #3 is\NMr. Nero, the newest member of CP9.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, though we are escorting criminals,\Nthere's no possibility of a raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just in case, we have military\Npower ready in each car, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on your side! Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:14:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foreman! It must be hard even to move, right?\NWhy don't you take a little break?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! This is nothing.\NHurry up and find those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone let Iceberg-san\Nknow what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two men went to give a report to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going? Iceberg-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Answer if you hear us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food... you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I want meat! Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to bring all the\Nmeat you can gather. Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why are we being slave-driven like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this isn't for that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best for Paulie-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who's devoted to her even after being dumped!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, she must be really hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a growing girl, I bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one, too. There really\Naren't any stores open right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. How about the kitchen\Nat the station's employee dining hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't take the backstreets.\NI bet the area is already flooded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we have no choice but\Nto search this area, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But--\N--Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that girl would forgive us\Nif we went back empty-handed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:17:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the strong winds are already\Ninterfering with my sense of smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, we've been calling out this much,\Nand yet there's no answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop saying stupid stuff! We'll just do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you guys? Luffy... Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys wouldn't be taken out\Nby a leopard man like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally know why Robin left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming to rescue you with\NLuffy and the others without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:18:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Paulie-san! Please take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more the water ebbs,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the bigger the returning wave becomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you see how the tide ebbs,\Nyou can tell the scale of the storm surge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if we try to see how much lower\Nthe water level goes this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that, Chimney.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! This is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea looks as if it dried up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I haven't seen a sight\Nlike this in the past few decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can the tide ebb this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:19:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen something like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how big of a wave is coming this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The backstreets are gonna\Nbe completely swallowed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any people\Nin the backstreets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there are, they'll die instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The roar of the sea... has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma! Look, look! There's something there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something between two houses!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Look! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're that pirate girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Pirate lady! Hey, look over there!\NThere's something there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is it you're going on about, Chimney?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this dried-up sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? That straw hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that your King of the Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:21:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go down to the backstreets!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.98,0:21:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Backstreets?! Hey, someone! Stop that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna lose your life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Laguna is already coming! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.74,0:22:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We had a dream that day{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.36,0:22:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our belief in ourselves{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.18,0:22:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}makes us able to cross the wildly surging ocean{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.26,0:22:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're braver and more caring than anyone else{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.61,0:22:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you ever depart this ship\Nand live in a different world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.86,0:23:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the end, we can all surely smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.13,0:23:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Luffy... Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, Nami! Well, I got completely\Nstuck when I got sent flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.63,0:23:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! Robin was lying to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.84,0:23:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? She was lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.06,0:23:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She sacrificed herself in order to protect us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! We'll protect Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.50,0:23:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nami's Soul Cries Out!\NStraw Hat Luffy Makes a Comeback!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.15,0:23:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
